[[Digital Performer]] has multiple levels of undo however they require the use of the Key Command '''Shift Z Command'''.

If you would like to make multiple levels on undo available by using the conventional '''Z Command''' , you can [[Digital Performer:Assigning key commands|reassign the key commands.]]

Go to the Commands window  '''Setup / Commands''' and reassign the command '''undo previous action''' to '''Command Z''' and either change or remove the command assigned to '''Undo/Redo'''.


